
bdog-stdjs used in addition to bdog-node provides haXe integration features and
standard library support

Status
------


Compiling with haxe
-------------------

You must add  -D nodejs to the compile line. 

From the top directory

haxe -cp . -D nodejs -js main.js -main tests.Main 

to compile main.js

and then to execute

node main.js

Compiling with haxed (a haxe package build, deploy and install tool)
--------------------------------------------------------------------

haxed build nodejs

